{"tid":585823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺新主場竟然無獎盃陳列室！","createTime":"2018-03-09T04:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T04:04:14.000Z","uid":4661,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5f73f848f9f9b27954368e40c83340426f9bf0","tid":585823,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"隨著熱刺新主場來季正式啟用，越來越多有關該場館的設計曝光，繼早前有報道指球場外圍將安裝LED燈牆，讓北倫敦的天空呈現一片「藍彩」後，球場的內部設計亦進一步曝光。英國《太陽報》報道，熱刺的新主場不但可以隨時延伸，成為欖球比賽場地外，據報還會在球員通道旁設有落地玻璃，讓球迷或貴賓觀看球員們步出球場的一刻。<br />\n<br />\n報道續指，球場內還會設有餐廳等，設施可謂應有盡有。不過《太陽報》發現，熱刺的內部設計未有設立安放獎盃的陳列室，似乎領隊普捷天奴和一眾球員，要繼續努力為熱刺增添獎盃，才有望令球會增設讓球迷自豪的獎盃陳列室了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520516998_13a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520516998_13a6.jpg&h=648065e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520517000_1b9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520517000_1b9e.jpg&h=0c3a350a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520517002_e55c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520517002_e55c.jpg&h=df924945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520517004_90d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520517004_90d5.jpg&h=1d9abd4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17f6c1e7b26eb3d90f57e16996e2df5bd03c1a00","tid":585823,"uid":158791,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"我熱唔需要獎盃證明自己"},{"pid":"648eeead33ef74b36337177093634827d80705a5","tid":585823,"uid":12660